        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>The Wellness Session Management System is a web-based application designed to manage wellness sessions efficiently. It allows users to book, track, and attend various wellness activities, such as yoga classes, fitness sessions, meditation workshops, and mental health seminars. Administrators can manage sessions, handle registrations, and promote health and wellness initiatives within a community.</p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Session Booking: Users can browse available wellness sessions and book slots according to their preferences.</li>
            <li>Admin Dashboard: Admins can create, modify, and track sessions, manage registrations, and promote upcoming events.</li>
            <li>Waitlist Management: In case of full bookings, users can join a waitlist and get promoted to a confirmed spot if space becomes available.</li>
            <li>QR Code Check-In: A secure and efficient check-in process using unique QR codes for attendees.</li>
            <li>Reminder & Notifications: Automated reminders and notifications sent to users about upcoming sessions and any changes.</li>
            <li>Feedback System: After attending a session, users can provide feedback to improve future wellness programs.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Real-Life Use Cases</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Corporate Wellness Programs: Companies offering health sessions for employees to promote well-being.</li>
            <li>Fitness Studios and Yoga Centers: Managing class bookings, session availability, and waitlists.</li>
            <li>Mental Health Workshops: Promoting mental wellness with session tracking and feedback.</li>
            <li>Public Wellness Initiatives: Organizing community wellness events with easy registration and participation.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>This project aims to create an accessible and organized platform for wellness providers and users, ensuring smooth management and active participation in wellness sessions.</p>

